### 2. The `.gitignore`

Save this exactly as `.gitignore` in the root of your project. The most important line here is `.env*.local`, which guarantees your Gemini and MongoDB keys stay private.

```text
# dependencies
/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.js

# testing
/coverage

# next.js
/.next/
/out/

# production
/build

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# local env files (CRITICAL: Do not remove these)
.env*.local
.env
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# vercel
.vercel